text: Fahad Ahmed (born 11 July 2001) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Twenty20 Cricket League on 25 February 2019. He made his List A debut for Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 23 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
